description: Maui is home to Donut Dynamite, and to say that its many fans “go nuts” for their gorgeously delicious variety of gourmet brioche donuts would just be the understatement of the year. Maple Bacon, Apple Crisp, S’more, DoNutella, Banana MacNut Crunch filled with banana cream... need we say more? If you’re not yet jonesing for these donuts with all your might, then there’s really just one reason: you haven’t yet delighted in Donut Dynamite.
name: Donut Dynamite
